	(text "ADC CONFIGURATION\n\nMD0 = LOW: I²C CONTROL MODE\nMS/AD = LOW: 7-BIT I²C ADDRESS 0x4A\n\nI²C1 PULL-UP PAIR IS SELECTED BY THE PD VARIANT;\nSEE MCU AND USB_PD SHEETS.\n\nI²S SLAVE; BCK PLL MODE IS USED WHEN SCKI IS ABSENT.\nTARGET AUDIO FORMAT: 48 kHz / 24-BIT."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 49.022 145.542 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "0de05433-ad72-482d-b95b-ba7fb79c67b4")
	)
	(text "OPTIONAL LINE-IN / ADC POPULATION GROUP\n\nLINE-IN BUILD:\nPOPULATE U3, R25-R30, C39-C49,\nD4, D8, PLUS J5 AND D5 ON DAUGHTER_IO.\n\nPLAYBACK-ONLY BUILD:\nDNP ALL COMPONENTS LISTED ABOVE.\n\nVARIANT FIELD = LINE_IN_OPTION\nI2C PULL-UP SELECTION IS CONTROLLED SEPARATELY\nBY THE PD / NO-PD OPTION."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 54.102 35.814 0)
